{"tid":1072144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[將來一定好睇過TVB] 兩子任聯席主席　接掌千億恒地王國","createTime":"2019-03-21T23:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T23:59:24.000Z","uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ce6b23d54fac0f94de52accd0a0b1a52f40c859","tid":1072144,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T23:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先重温下呢間野有幾仆街<br />\n[有錢大撚曬有錢有特權] 恒基兆業正仆街新聞重温<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/990925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/990925</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一定爭家產爭到含家產</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n現年56歲的李兆基長子李家傑，以及48歲的幼子李家誠之前均為恒地副主席，恒地今次無交代誰是決策上的「最高領導人」及日後分工。現時大致由長子管中國業務，幼子管香港業務。有指李兆基早年常帶着李家誠在身邊教導，對他較為寵愛。李兆基退任主席後仍留任公司董事，有關決定及安排於5月28日股東周年大會交代。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聯席主席 一正好撚勁 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190321/20638200?fbclid=IwAR0NCt4nNmJ4x1XA4SjBKfAgOtfKfysUHp3Z8EfwAsB73Z3FF3AOGqLLD7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190321%2F20638200%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0NCt4nNmJ4x1XA4SjBKfAgOtfKfysUHp3Z8EfwAsB73Z3FF3AOGqLLD7E&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=425caa12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190321%2F20638200%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0NCt4nNmJ4x1XA4SjBKfAgOtfKfysUHp3Z8EfwAsB73Z3FF3AOGqLLD7E&h=daf35c8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190321/20638200?fbclid=IwAR0NCt4nNmJ4x1XA4SjBKfAgOtfKfysUHp3Z8